---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Hero from "../../components/Hero.astro";
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import WebsitesImage from "../../assets/service-accessibility.png";
---

<Layout title="MWL - Accessibility">
  <Hero page="Accessibility"></Hero>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-8 mt-12">
    <h2 class="md:text-4xl text-3xl font-bold text-slate-50 mb-4 underline decoration-solid decoration-2 decoration-yellow-400 underline-offset-8">Accessibility</h2>
    <!--Image and description container -->
    <div class="flex xl:flex-nowrap flex-wrap xl:gap-10 gap-4">
      <div class="xl:w-1/2 w-full">
        <Image src={WebsitesImage} class="max-w-full rounded-lg" alt="wireframes illustrating the prototype of a website" />
      </div>
      <div class="xl:w-1/2 w-full">
        <p class="mb-4 text-slate-50 xl:text-xl md:text-lg text-base">
          Are you reaching all your users?Countless individuals worldwide navigate their lives with disabilities. 
          The spectrum of these disabilities varies widely, and not all impede one's capacity to engage with the digital realm.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4 text-slate-50 xl:text-xl md:text-lg text-base">
          Yet, numerous disabilities pose challenges, constructing hurdles for individuals when it comes to navigating and comprehending certain web pages.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4 text-slate-50 xl:text-xl md:text-lg text-base">
          Incorporating diverse accessibility practices becomes paramount, ensuring inclusivity and broadening the reach of your website to the widest possible audience.
        </p>
        <div class="flex xl:mt-20 mt-8">
					<a href="/contact" class="mwl-background shadow-3xl md:text-2xl text-xl text-center p-3 text-white border-black rounded-full border-solid border w-64 transition-transform transform-gpu hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg">Get in touch</a>
				</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!--List of typical service including -->
    <div class="text-slate-50 py-40">
      <h3 class="xl:text-4xl text-3xl font-bold mb-4">What a typical Accessibility service includes:</h3>
      <ul class="md:text-xl text-lg list-disc pl-6">
        <li>Overview of your current solutionâ€™s accessibility</li>
        <li>HTML optimization for accessibility</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .mwl-background{
    background-color: var(--mwl-purple);
  }
</style>